= Cards


== Object

[cols="2,1,5"]
|===
|Name |Type |Description

|`id` | `int` | unique identifier
|`owner_type` | `string` | What type of entity owns the card.  Possible values: `parent`, `kid`.
|`owner_id` | `int` | unique identifier of the owner entity.
|`name_on_card` | `string` |
|`number` | `string` |
|`expiration_date` | `date` | When the card expires.  Day can be ignored.
|`type` | `string` | See https://developer.visa.com/guides/request_response_codes#Card_Type for possible values.
|`sub_type` | `string` | See https://developer.visa.com/guides/request_response_codes#Card_Sub_Type for possible values.
|`amount_on_card` | `number` |
|`amount_spent` | `number` |
|===

